Title: On off-shell bosonic string amplitudes
Authors: L. Cappiello, R. Marotta, R. Pettorino and F. Pezzella (Dipartimento
  di Scienze Fisiche, Universita' di Napoli and INFN, Sezione di Napoli)
Comments: 12 pages, Latex. One reference added. Introduction and conclusions
  expanded. Some other minor changes in the text
Report-no: DSFTH 11/98
Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A13 (1998) 2433-2444
\\
  We give a simple prescription for computing, in the framework of the bosonic
string theory, off-shell one-loop amplitudes with any number of external
massless particles, both for the open and for the closed string. We discuss
their properties and, in particular, for the two-string one-loop amplitudes we
show their being transverse.
